source: TEXT_CTSMJIORCHESTRION_00808_SYSTEM_000_100<tab>The orchestrion may only be accessed and heard by the owner of an island.
target: TEXT_CTSMJIORCHESTRION_00808_SYSTEM_000_100<tab>Si vous n'êtes pas pro<var 16 /var>prié<var 16 /var>taire de l'île, vous ne pouvez ni changer ni entendre les musiques.

source: TEXT_CTSMJIORCHESTRION_00808_SYSTEM_000_000<tab>This appears to be the orchestrion belonging to this island's owner.
target: TEXT_CTSMJIORCHESTRION_00808_SYSTEM_000_000<tab>Les visiteurs ne sont pas autorisés à utiliser l'orchestrion.
